::KitKat::

She looked at Terrorsaur. "Crazy? Possably, these maximals are either 
stupid or insane compared to me right now."  She fired on Deemos 
again.

She was knocked down by a hit to her shoulder.  She slowly got up and 
took her rifle back in her hands and fires again.  She was feeling 
almost euphoric from the lack of meck fluid.  She was standing in a 
growing puddle of her own mech fluid.  She didn't care about the pain 
surging through her body.  She only knew that these bots were 
attacking and she needed to defend her base, her friends and crew 
members.  

*Autoguns firing on all maximal signatures*
